"```sql\nSELECT a.account_id\nFROM account a\nJOIN client c ON a.account_id = disp.account_id\nJOIN disp d ON c.client_id = d.client_id\nJOIN district di ON c.district_id = di.district_id\nWHERE c.gender = 'F'\nORDER BY c.birth_date ASC, di.A11 ASC\nLIMIT 1;\n``` \n\nThis SQL query selects the account numbers of female clients who are the oldest (earliest birth date) and have the lowest average salary. It joins the necessary tables based on the foreign key relationships and filters for female clients. The results are ordered by birth date and average salary, and it limits the output to the top result."